\": 839}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A fleet of barges took the competitors on a 6km stretch of the river alongside some of the French capital\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s most famous landmarks, as performers recreated some of the sports to be showcased in the Games on floating platforms.\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 1069, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 933, \"end\": 939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9973145484235338, \"rank\": 0.0025206461430411103, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A fleet\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 849}, {\"ngram\": \"barges\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 859}, {\"ngram\": \"the competitors\", \"from\": 865, \"to\": 880}, {\"ngram\": \"a 6km stretch\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 897}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 910}, {\"ngram\": \"most famous landmarks\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 973}, {\"ngram\": \"performers\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 988}, {\"ngram\": \"the sports\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1017}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1046}, {\"ngram\": \"floating platforms\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1068}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was the first time that an opening ceremony has taken place outside a stadium, adding to the headaches for a vast security operation, just hours aftera sabotage attack on the high-speed TGV rail networkcaused travel chaos across France.\", \"from\": 1071, \"to\": 1310, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1260, \"end\": 1263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TGV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"TGV\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TGV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TGV\"}, {\"begin\": 1303, \"end\": 1309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999999563443, \"rank\": 3.265389781670281e-11, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1092}, {\"ngram\": \"an opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1117}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1133}, {\"ngram\": \"a stadium\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1151}, {\"ngram\": \"the headaches\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1176}, {\"ngram\": \"a vast security operation\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1206}, {\"ngram\": \"just hours aftera sabotage attack\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1241}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI invite everybody: dream with us.\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1349, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everybody\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1333}, {\"ngram\": \"dream\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1340}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1346, \"to\": 1348}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like the Olympic athletes, be inspired with the joy that only sport can give us.\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1430, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic athletes\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1375}, {\"ngram\": \"the joy\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1401}, {\"ngram\": \"only sport\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1417}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1429}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us celebrate this Olympic spirit of living in peace,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d International Olympics Committee president Thomas Bach said, as the ceremony came to an end at the foot of the Eiffel Tower.\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1615, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1534, \"end\": 1545, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thomas Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1437}, {\"ngram\": 